:{{DIcon|undefined}} Celine's recent troubles...
:::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 301140101: Config/Level/Mission/3011401/Act/Act301140101.json-->
:::'''Celine:''' I'm happy with my lot at the moment, dubbing voices for Tamila and being her shadow. What's wrong with that?
:::'''Celine:''' But yeah... I can't help thinking sometimes how wonderful it must be to stand in that spotlight like Tamila... how wonderful it must feel...
:::'''Celine:''' So I've been watching Tamila's sparkling on-stage performances, like a painter copying a famous painting, trying to copy everything Tamila does...
:::'''Celine:''' But! Even though I can perfectly emulate all of Tamila's behaviors, I'm still lacking that key piece of her soul...
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Soul?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_301140107-->
:::'''Celine:''' Yeah, soul... my mimicry's already pretty much perfect, but the presence and gravitas contained in all those micro-expressions is something I haven't been able to master...
:::'''Celine:''' I know that anyone can just copy her body as long as you practice hard enough... but I'll need to copy her soul if I want to truly become Tamila.
:::'''Celine:''' Can you help me?
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Stealing souls is black magic, and forbidden...
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_301140111-->
::::'''Celine:''' Oh dear. No! I'm not a witch. Why would you say it like that?
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} How can I help you?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_301140113-->
::::'''Celine:''' Well... don't worry. It's not a difficult job~
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Then I will do my best!
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_301140115-->
::::'''Celine:''' Ah, that makes me so happy! Thank you~
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_301140116-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_301140116-->
:::'''Celine:''' I would like you to visit the store where Tamila often goes and ask the staff in secret what Tamila's likes and hobbies are beyond the limelight.
:::'''Celine:''' Perhaps if I can learn what those are, then I can understand a bit more about Tamila's soul.
:::'''Celine:''' And with that, I'll be able to be like Tamila and shine brightly onstage.
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_301140101_29-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_301140101_29-->
:::{{DIcon|Talk}} Can't you just go yourself?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_301140120-->
